                            <p>
                                Discover pets available for adoption and find your perfect match today.

                            </p>
                            <a class="text-primary text-uppercase" href="">Read More<i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="service-item bg-light d-flex p-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-heart display-1 text-primary me-4"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="text-uppercase mb-3">Filter by common interests</h5>
                            <p>Match with pets that share similar habits and energy levels with you.</p>
                            <a class="text-primary text-uppercase" href="">Read More<i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
